      • reply

        Publication reply(String message)
        Sends a reply to this message. If the the message did not contain a replyTo field, a NatsException will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        message - the message with which to reply to the sender
        Returns:
        a Publication instance representing the pending reply operation
        Throws:
        NatsException - if the message did not contain a replyTo field

      • reply

        Publication reply(String message,
                long delay,
                TimeUnit unit)
        Sends a reply to this message after the specified delay has passed. This method returns immediate and sends the delayed response asynchronously. If the the message did not contain a replyTo field, a NatsException will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        message - the message with which to reply to the sender
        delay - the amount of time to wait before sending the reply
        unit - the time unit of the delay argument
        Returns:
        a Publication instance representing the pending reply operation
        Throws:
        NatsException - if the message did not contain a replyTo field
